snippet.title: BBQ Pit Boys
snippet.description: YouTube's #1 Channel for BBQ and Grilling with 850+ instructional recipes on video, 340 million video views, and over 5 million Subscribers and Followers across Social Media platforms. Watch the BBQ Pit Boys demonstrate the techniques for cooking up some classic barbecue and grilling recipes, show you what BBQ tools you'll need, how to select the correct cuts of meat for the grill or smoker, and the tips and tricks on how to be a Pitmaster. Sign-up, join, or form a BBQ Pit Boys Chapter, by heading on over to our Website -now over 18,000 member Chapters in 100+ countries Worldwide. Contact us below or head on over to our website. Business inquiries welcomed.!
